snippet.title: Huntdown Collector's Edition, Limited Run Games
snippet.description:
Now available on PS4, Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, Windows, MAC, Linux, iOS and Android.
Get it here: 
Switch: https://limitedrungames.com/products/huntdown-switch
PS4: https://limitedrungames.com/products/huntdown-ps4

Download a free demo of Huntdown here (buy it if you like it once):
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1198183067
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.coffeestain.huntdown
